{"tid":2086690,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"很多事情不是看到希望才去堅持，而是堅持了才看得到希望","createTime":"2020-06-30T11:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T15:47:03.000Z","uid":224827,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a448fd5d734f20d6a44bb7ce513f7957e0644d6","tid":2086690,"uid":224827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"明天怎麼你還是不知道<br />\n過咗一年有多，呢個社會所發生嘅事一日比一日快<br />\n<br />\n我哋可能都曾經同身邊嘅人過住一啲吃喝玩樂嘅生活，但係呢一年多，一切既野都變得不一樣，<br />\n一路走來，身體、心靈都早已變得傷痕累累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏入7月1號，人心惶惶，呢個日子究竟會發生咩事，冇人會知<br />\n<br />\n我相信呢一刻大家都有好多擔心或者憂慮，但同時間好多人都好想繼續向前行，前面可能係佈滿荊棘，可能係迂迴曲折，可能係冇盡頭、甚至係無回頭嘅路.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但請你記得我地互相支持着，絕對唔係一個人，而係一班人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到呢一日我想借助呢個平台俾大家喺度留低你哋嘅心聲，無論係喜與悲 都歡迎你喺度留言，多一個聲音，就係多一份力量<br />\n<br />\n撐住呀，手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8259f413a36a87ff51db0a9528821e45c5bf7c3","tid":2086690,"uid":224827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d89a8c82e31b1ff414f4e09a4661d87a863a0ca","tid":2086690,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hva5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74Hva5.png&h=a1d38e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4062cd2e9b88f0ee44278c8b30e14db839a3781","tid":2086690,"uid":44388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">7.1 全民電子英美旗 Sir This E-Way!<br /